Variation.
The position of the dorsal black spot on the forewing is variable. A specimen from Thailand has the spot at the distal 1/5 of the cell beyond the black spot on the dorsum (
Moriuti 1982a
), which resembles that of specimens from Yunnan Province. Specimens from Hainan Province have the spot displaced inwards and immediately above the spot on the dorsum (
Fig. 73
).
